SDL3PP_ALPHA_OPAQUE.doc:
A fully opaque 8-bit alpha value.

@since This macro is available since SDL 3.2.0.

@sa SDL3PP_ALPHA_TRANSPARENT

SDL3PP_ALPHA_OPAQUE_FLOAT.doc:
A fully opaque floating point alpha value.

@since This macro is available since SDL 3.2.0.

